caption: In the foreground, a man stands upon a rocky precipice with his back to the viewer. He is wrapped in a dark green overcoat, and grips a walking stick in his right hand. His hair caught in a wind, the wanderer gazes out on a landscape covered in a thick sea of fog. In the middle ground, several other ridges, perhaps not unlike the ones the wanderer himself stands upon, jut out from the mass. Through the wreaths of fog, forests of trees can be perceived atop these escarpments. In the far distance, faded mountains rise in the left, gently leveling off into lowland plains in the right. Beyond here, the pervading fog stretches out indefinitely, eventually commingling with the horizon and becoming indistinguishable from the cloud-filled sky.
caption_zh: 在前景中，一个男人背对着观众站在岩石悬崖上。 他穿着深绿色的大衣，右手握着一根手杖。 流浪者的头发被风吹起，凝视着外面被浓浓雾海覆盖的风景。 在中间地带，其他几座山脊从人群中伸出，也许与流浪者本人站立的山脊没有什么不同。 透过浓雾，可以看到悬崖顶上的树林。 在远处，褪色的山脉在左边升起，在右边缓缓地变成低地平原。 越过这里，弥漫的雾气无限延伸，最终与地平线融为一体，与布满云彩的天空变得难以区分。

caption: In a dystopian grocery store of the future, a lone woman stands amidst towering shelves of food items, their packaging and branding all but unrecognizable. The shelves themselves are adorned with synthetic vines and flowers, creating a hauntingly surreal atmosphere. The woman is dressed in a tattered outfit made of kale leaves, hinting at a world where even the most basic of necessities are hard to come by. A small bird perches on her shoulder, its chirping echoing through the otherwise silent space. Despite the eerie surroundings, the woman appears unfazed, a testament to the resilience of the human spirit in a world that's lost its way. This still shot from a Blade Runner 2049-esque world defies the mundane, plain, and ordinary, evoking a sense of bleak, otherworldly beauty.
caption_zh: 在未来的反乌托邦杂货店里，一个孤独的女人站在高耸的食品货架中间，它们的包装和品牌几乎无法辨认。 架子本身装饰着合成藤蔓和花朵，营造出一种令人难以忘怀的超现实氛围。 这名女子穿着羽衣甘蓝叶制成的破烂衣服，暗示着一个连最基本的必需品都难以获得的世界。 一只小鸟停在她的肩上，叽叽喳喳的叫声在寂静的空间里回荡。 尽管周围环境诡异，这位女士却显得泰然自若，这证明了人类精神在迷失方向的世界中的韧性。 这张静态照片来自《银翼杀手 2049》式的世界，挑战了世俗、朴素和平凡，唤起了一种荒凉、超凡脱俗的美感。
